name: Sexy Wedding Short Dress
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Training settings:

39 images, 15 steps, 14 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.3-0.7 (0.4 best results in my experiments)

  • Keys: SWSD, FLWR, NOFLWR, back view, inside church

Keywords:

  • SWSD is the main keywords, necessary, always use it, might be necessary to use a weight 1.3-1.5. It stands for Sexy Wedding Short Dress

  • FLWR is an optional keyword, might need to use a weight on it 1.2-1.7. It stands for Flower and by using it you will end with a dress with many flower decorations.

  • NOFLWR it's the opposite of FLWR but doesn't always work, might need a bigger weight

  • back view, inside church these are self explanatory.

Also, you might want a not white dress, in this case you can add stuff like "red dress" or "black dress".

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
